room add 800 500 1000 office
with light
cursor save spawn

room add 200 300 400 corridor z++
room add 600 400 600 office z++
with light
cursor save branch-point
room add 1000 300 200 corridor x--
room add 400 400 400 office x--
with light

room add 200 200 100 broken-wall y z--

